values: in between buses morning phone cam opportunities this is why days should start at 6am bird...and? a little more emphasis on neon skies

Yesterday it snowed!
Snow in November is possibly a first.

Up on Marquam Hill there were proper big flakes. I have a photo (as always) but can't upload today for some reason.
Watch this space.......

A proper cup of tea tastes amazing after 3 months of not being able to have any. Hurray for hideously overpriced 'world market' stores. Cadburys and Mcvitties too. Did you know that here people don't know what Christmas Crackers are? Imagine that.......

Nala This is for size comparison (she's teeny) She peed on me yesterday (actually made a point of crawling onto my lap just to do that). Shawn just carried her off the sofa because she smells like "impending poop" (BEST PHRASE EVER, surely). Hopefully these issues will be resolved shorly.
We got a kitty... I want some suggestions for names! (she's a girl).
Autumn in Oregon nice huh?
